CSCB07 Tutorial Exercise #2

This repository contains my work for CSCB07 Software Design Tutorial Exercise #2.

In this exercise, I updated the Polynomial class from Exercise 1 to use two arrays:
- one array for non-zero coefficients
- one array for the corresponding exponents

The updated Polynomial class now supports:
- polynomial addition
- polynomial multiplication
- polynomial evaluation
- root checking
- reading a polynomial from a file
- saving a polynomial to a file

This exercise also practices Git branching by creating and working on a separate branch named lab2.

Files included:
- Polynomial.java
- Driver.java
- info